videos.description: Daniel Hamilton leads the UConn fast break before making the pass to Amida Brimah for a massive one-handed slam.
videos.headline: There's huge dunks, and then there's a huge dunk from Brimah

videos.description: UConn coach Kevin Ollie says that the heart and want to play for each other was the key for the Huskies to get through peaks and valleys of the season to win the AAC tournament title.
videos.headline: Ollie: Team playing for each other and with heart

videos.description: Connecticut takes down Memphis 72-58 to win the American Conference tournament tile for the first time in school history.
videos.headline: UConn rolls by Memphis, wins first American title
